---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Komodo Labs"
  description="Software engineer, builder, and founder with 8+ years across Web3, fintech, and AI. Founder of Komodo Labs."
>
<style>

  /* LAYOUT */
  .about {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    padding: 72px 0 100px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* SIDEBAR */
  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 40px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.1s both;
  }

  .headshot-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .headshot-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    display: block;
  }

  .sidebar-name {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .sidebar-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--neon);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .sidebar-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .sidebar-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .sidebar-link:hover { color: var(--white); }

  .sidebar-link svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* CONTENT */
  .content {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.2s both;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .content h1 {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .bio p {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .bio p strong {
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .bio p.highlight {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 400;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--neon);
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .bio .closing {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--gray-200);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .headshot-wrap {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .sidebar {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="wrapper">

  <Nav />

  <div class="about">

    <!-- SIDEBAR -->
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="headshot-wrap">
        <img src="/headshot.jpg" alt="Chase" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="sidebar-name">Chase Brown</div>
        <div class="sidebar-title">Engineer &amp; Founder</div>
        <div class="sidebar-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/chasebrownn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="sidebar-link">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0 1 12 6.844a9.59 9.59 0 0 1 2.504.337c1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.02 10.02 0 0 0 22 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"/></svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chase-brown-41a934173/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="sidebar-link">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 0 1-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 1 1 2.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:chase@komodolabs.io" class="sidebar-link">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 7 10-7"/></svg>
            chase@komodolabs.io
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- BIO -->
    <main class="content">
      <div class="section-label">About</div>
      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <div class="bio">
        <p class="highlight">
          I'm a software engineer, builder, and founder with over 8 years of experience designing and deploying production-grade systems across Web3, fintech, and now AI.
        </p>

        <p>
          I got my start while earning my Computer Science degree, where I founded <strong>Elevate Software</strong> — a development shop focused on building full-stack applications for emerging DeFi projects. What began as a college side venture quickly turned into a 3-year journey of shipping real products, working directly with founders, and learning what it actually takes to bring ideas from zero to production.
        </p>

        <p>
          That experience shaped how I approach engineering today: practical, product-driven, and deeply focused on execution.
        </p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>
          Since then, I've spent the last several years operating as a <strong>Senior / Lead Smart Contract Engineer</strong>, working with financial institutions, hedge funds, and high-growth crypto-native teams. I've led the design and deployment of complex on-chain systems across multiple blockchains — building everything from stablecoin architectures and staking vaults to cross-chain infrastructure and liquidity systems. Across the protocols I've contributed to, I've helped secure and scale systems responsible for tens of millions in TVL, with a strong emphasis on security, reliability, and long-term maintainability.
        </p>

        <p>
          My work sits at the intersection of engineering, product, and systems design. I don't just write code — I think through how systems behave in production, how users interact with them, and how teams can operate and scale around them.
        </p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>
          At my core, <strong>I'm a builder.</strong>
        </p>

        <p>
          I've always been drawn to the process of taking an idea, shaping it into something tangible, and pushing it all the way to deployment. Whether it's launching a DeFi protocol, designing infrastructure for financial systems, or building internal tools that automate entire workflows, I care about creating things that actually get used.
        </p>

        <p>
          Recently, I've been going deep into <strong>AI and automation</strong>, helping businesses integrate AI into their operations to unlock efficiency, better decision-making, and entirely new capabilities. From workflow automation to intelligent systems layered on top of existing products, I'm focused on helping companies not just experiment with AI — but actually implement it in ways that drive real outcomes.
        </p>

        <p>
          Alongside client work, I'm actively building my own AI-powered products and tools — continuing the same pattern that's defined my career: identify leverage, build systems, and ship.
        </p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>
          Through <strong>Komodo Labs</strong>, I partner with companies to design, build, and scale software across Web3 and AI. Whether it's architecting a protocol, integrating AI into business workflows, or bringing a new product to life, my goal is always the same:
        </p>

        <p class="closing">
          Build systems that work, scale, and last.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>

  </div>

  <Footer />

</div>

</Layout>
